<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_1092162">卷轴学家&nbsp; 10级<br>法师<br>前置要求：在手艺上有专家熟练度<br>妳在日常准备中，可以创造两个两个临时卷轴，卷轴内的奥术法术需来自妳的法术书。这些卷轴的规则与一般卷轴相同(P.564)，但有一些额外限制。每个卷轴内含的法术环级必须不同，<span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color">并且内含法术的环级必须是二环，或至少要低于妳所能施展的最高环级。</span>妳用这种方式制作的卷轴在你下次进行日常准备时，会自动变成非魔法物品。临时卷轴没有任何价值。<br><br>During your daily preparations, you can create two temporary <br>scrolls containing arcane spells from your spellbook. These <br>scrolls follow the normal rules for scrolls (page 564), with some <br>additional restrictions.<span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color"> Each scroll must be of a different spell <br>level, and both spell levels must be 2 or more levels lower than <br>your highest-level spell. </span>Any scrolls you create this way become <br>non-magical the next time you make your daily preparations. A <br>temporary scroll has no value.<br><br>此处应当是<span style="color: red;" class="bbc_color">至少低于你最高环级2级</span></div>
</div>
</div>
