<div class="inner" id="msg_1122269">补上专长中英比对<br><br>1级专长<br>反制法术(COUNTERSPELL) [[R]] 1级 <br>施法免材(ESCHEW MATERIALS) 1级<br>魔宠(FAMILIAR) 1级<br>学徒之手(HAND OF THE APPRENTICE) 1级<br>及远法术(REACH SPELL) [[A]] 1级<br>扩展法术(WIDEN SPELL) [[A]] 1级<br><br>2级专长<br>戏法扩增(CANTRIP EXPANSION) 2级<br>藏匿法术(CONCEAL SPELL) [[A]] 2级<br>强化魔宠(ENHANCED FAMILIAR)<br><br>4级专长<br>附法武器(BESPELL WEAPON) [[F]] 4级<br>连结专攻(LINKED FOCUS) 4级<br>默发法术(SILENT SPELL) [[A]] 4级<br><br>6级专长<br>法术穿透(SPELL PENETRATION) 6级<br>镇定施法(STEADY SPELLCASTING) 6级<br><br>8级专长<br>进阶学派法术(ADVANCED SCHOOL SPELL) 8级<br>连接保能(BOND CONSERVATION) [[A]] 8级<br>万法归一(UNIVERSAL VERSATILITY) 8级<br><br>10级专长<br>强能(OVERWHELMING ENERGY) [[A]] 10级<br>瞬发施法(QUICKENED CASTING) [[F]] 10级<br>卷轴学家(SCROLL SAVANT) 10级<br><br>12级专长<br>精巧反制法术(CLEVER COUNTERSPELL) 12级<br>魔法感知(MAGIC SENSE) 12级<br><br>14级专长<br>连结专精(BONDED FOCUS) 14级<br>反射法术(REFLECT SPELL) 14级<br>高级连结(SUPERIOR BOND) 14级<br><br>16级专长<br>随意专注(EFFORTLESS CONCENTRATION) [[F]] 16级<br>法术弥补(SPELL TINKER) [[AA]] 16级<br><br>18级专长<br>无限可能(INFINITE POSSIBILITIES) 18级<br>重备法术(REPREPARE SPELL) 18级<br><br>20级专长<br>大法师之力(ARCHWIZARD’S MIGHT) 20级<br>超魔宗师(METAMAGIC MASTERY) 20级<br>法术融合(SPELL COMBINATION) 20级</div>
